{"talk":{"id":1854,"name":"Xavier Vilalta: Architecture at home in its community","description":"When TED Fellow Xavier Vilalta was commissioned to create a multistory shopping mall in Addis Ababa, he panicked. Other centers represented everything he hated about contemporary architecture: wasteful, glass towers requiring tons of energy whose design had absolutely nothing to do with Africa. In this charming talk, Vilalta shows how he champions an alternative approach: to harness nature, reference design tradition and create beautiful, modern, iconic buildings fit for a community.","slug":"xavier_vilalta_architecture_at_home_in_its_community","recorded_at":"2013-06-11 00:00:00","published_at":"2013-10-25 15:00:08","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:46:29","viewed_count":1032960,"emailed_count":92,"event":{"id":241,"name":"TEDGlobal 2013"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/45a5d32a2b066d669f6a3310014934ff480339bc_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/45a5d32a2b066d669f6a3310014934ff480339bc_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/45a5d32a2b066d669f6a3310014934ff480339bc_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"1600x1200","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/45a5d32a2b066d669f6a3310014934ff480339bc_1600x1200.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":false,"media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/XavierVilalta_2013G-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":3824525,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/XavierVilalta_2013G-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":10533555,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/XavierVilalta_2013G-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":18773025,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/Xavier